  <brief_title>Evaluation of a Closed-Loop Control System for Administering Patient-Specific Anesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of a Closed-Loop Control System for Patient-Specific Induction and Maintenance of Propofol Hypnosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
